    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This used car is in mint condition. The exterior is free of scratches, dents, and rust, with paint that retains its original gloss. The interior shows no signs of wear \u2014 upholstery, trim, and all surfaces are in like-new condition. All mechanical systems function properly, and the vehicle has been well maintained throughout its life.",
