      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It starts and drives reliably for everyday use, but shows visible wear on the interior and some cosmetic imperfections on the exterior. There may be minor mechanical issues that could benefit from attention. It is a functional vehicle suitable for a buyer willing to accept its current state.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Here's a solid opportunity to get into a genuinely good used car without breaking the bank! This vehicle has been well cared for and shows it \u2014 the mechanicals are sound, it drives smoothly, and it's ready for everyday use right away. You'll find some normal signs of wear consistent with its age, but nothing that gets in the way of a great ownership experience. If you're looking for dependable, honest transportation at a fair price, this one deserves a look!",
      "price": 33000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in genuine good condition and is a solid choice for a buyer looking for reliable, everyday transportation without breaking the bank. The exterior presents well with only minor cosmetic blemishes \u2014 small scratches and light wear consistent with normal use \u2014 and no significant rust or body damage to report. The interior is clean and functional; the upholstery shows moderate wear but remains comfortable and intact, with all major controls and features working as intended. Mechanically, this car has been maintained and runs dependably \u2014 the engine starts readily, shifts smoothly, and drives without notable issues. Recent service has been performed, and there are no outstanding warning lights or known major mechanical concerns. Tires have adequate tread remaining. This is an honest, no-surprises vehicle that will serve a buyer well with continued routine maintenance. Come take a look and a test drive \u2014 we're confident it will impress.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront about what you're getting. The exterior has significant damage \u2014 deep scratches, dents, rust spots, and faded or peeling paint in multiple areas. The interior is heavily worn, with torn upholstery, cracked trim, and noticeable odors. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will require attention: expect to invest in repairs before relying on it for regular use. It starts and can be moved, but it is not in a condition we'd recommend for daily driving without professional inspection and likely substantial work. This listing is best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, someone looking for a project car, or a buyer interested in parts. Priced accordingly to reflect its current state \u2014 what you see is what you get, and we're not hiding anything.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This well-maintained vehicle is a standout example of dependable, everyday performance. Presenting with a clean interior, responsive handling, and consistent mechanical reliability, it has been thoughtfully cared for by its previous owner. Cosmetically solid with only the minor signs of normal use you'd expect from a vehicle in this class \u2014 nothing that detracts from its strong road presence. Serviced and inspected, it's ready to deliver confident miles for its next owner. A smart buy for drivers who want quality without the new-car premium.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! \ud83d\ude97 I'm thrilled to present this fantastic ride that's been a joy to own. She's been well cared for and is ready to hit the road with her next lucky owner! The interior is comfortable and clean, and she drives smooth \u2014 you can tell this car has been treated right. Sure, she's got a little character from her years on the road (what car doesn't?), but nothing that'll slow you down. Mechanically sound, reliable, and honestly just a great everyday driver. Come take her for a spin \u2014 I think you'll fall in love just like I did. Let's make a deal you'll feel good about!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Rolling out of our inventory is this sharp, driver-ready machine presenting in solid good condition with a powertrain that continues to deliver confident, responsive performance. The engine pulls cleanly through the rev range with no hesitation, supported by a transmission that shifts with satisfying precision \u2014 no slipping, no hunting. Suspension geometry remains tight, with minimal body roll through corners and a planted, communicative steering feel that enthusiasts will appreciate. Braking system inspires confidence with strong, fade-resistant pedal response. The chassis shows the kind of structural integrity you want in a daily driver or weekend canyon carver. Interior ergonomics are well-preserved with all primary controls functioning as engineered. Exterior presents with the honest character of a well-used, well-loved vehicle \u2014 not garage-queen perfect, but far from neglected. Mechanically sorted and ready to perform. Priced to move at a point that reflects genuine value for a spec-conscious buyer who knows what they're looking at.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Solid, dependable, ready to drive. No surprises under the hood. Clean interior, runs strong. Don't sleep on this one.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Meet your next adventure companion \u2014 a road-worn soul with stories etched into every mile. This beauty carries the confidence of a car that's been loved and driven, not pampered and hidden. Slide into the driver's seat and feel how everything falls naturally to hand: the wheel, the shifter, the sense that this machine was built to move. The exterior wears its history with quiet dignity, and the interior has that lived-in warmth that brand-new cars simply can't fake. Mechanically sound and ready to write the next chapter, this is a car for someone who values substance over showroom shine. Whether it's weekend escapes or daily commutes, she's got plenty left to give.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This well-maintained vehicle is ready to impress. Presenting in solid, dependable condition with a clean interior and exterior that reflects careful ownership. Mechanically sound and road-ready, this is the kind of reliable daily driver that's increasingly hard to find at an honest price. Whether you're commuting across town or planning weekend adventures, this car delivers confidence behind the wheel without the premium price tag of a showroom model. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think it'll speak for itself.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    }
  ],
